  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100210/extras/24f54d3f146d15ac5883d405750891b8.avif?t=1768578720\" width=657 height=258 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100210/extras/1f6507a8cbeb38508b9c50fd1a11a52a.avif?t=1768578720\" width=601 height=174 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >My Sweet Housemate is an interactive visual novel style game that puts you into the shoes of a homeless adult struggling to find affordable housing in America. You're hit with a stroke of good - or maybe bad - luck when you finally find a totally not suspicious rental listing for a room in an apartment. The only catch is that your new landlord, Seung-min, seems to have something off about him.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100210/extras/d0eb8f3931ecc4a4eaee609d290b08e7.avif?t=1768578720\" width=619 height=509 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find out more in this deliciously horrifying experience!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100210/extras/a0bd76fab7516abf74e36e1c649b9c6f.avif?t=1768578720\" width=601 height=174 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Character customisation that includes name, pronouns and voice</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choice, exploration and mini-game based gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple endings, replayability and in-game achievements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1-2 hours of comedy-filled gameplay</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100210/extras/24f54d3f146d15ac5883d405750891b8.avif?t=1768578720\" width=657 height=258 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100210/extras/1f6507a8cbeb38508b9c50fd1a11a52a.avif?t=1768578720\" width=601 height=174 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >My Sweet Housemate is an interactive visual novel style game that puts you into the shoes of a homeless adult struggling to find affordable housing in America. You're hit with a stroke of good - or maybe bad - luck when you finally find a totally not suspicious rental listing for a room in an apartment. The only catch is that your new landlord, Seung-min, seems to have something off about him.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100210/extras/d0eb8f3931ecc4a4eaee609d290b08e7.avif?t=1768578720\" width=619 height=509 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find out more in this deliciously horrifying experience!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100210/extras/a0bd76fab7516abf74e36e1c649b9c6f.avif?t=1768578720\" width=601 height=174 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Character customisation that includes name, pronouns and voice</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choice, exploration and mini-game based gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple endings, replayability and in-game achievements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1-2 hours of comedy-filled gameplay</p></li></ul>",
